text: Ream Andaeuk Commune () is a khum (commune) in Kiri Vong District, Takéo Province, Cambodia. == Administration == As of 2019, Ream Andaeuk Commune has 8 phums (villages) as follows. {| class="wikitable sortable mw-collapsible" !No. !Code !Village !Khmer |- !1 |21041001 |Svay Sa |ស្វាយស |- !2 |21041002 |Trayueng |ត្រយឹង |- !3 |21041003 |Trapeang Run |ត្រពាំងរុន |- !4 |21041004 |Ream Andaeuk |រាមអណ្ដើក |- !5 |21041005 |Trapeang Khchau |ត្រពាំងខ្ចៅ |- !6 |21041006 |Kaoh Kosal |កោះកុសល |- !7 |21041007 |Kouk Roka |គោករកា |- !8 |21041008 |Pongro |ពង្រ |} == References == Category:Communes of Takeo Province Category:Kiri Vong District
